msgstr "Bloķēts (Pro)"

#: frontend/src/metabase/admin/permissions/components/DataPermissionsHelp/DataPermissionsHelp.tsx:85
msgid "The group cannot view any data from the data source, even if they have collection access to view questions or dashboards that draw from that data."
msgstr "Grupa nevar skatīt nekādus datus no datu avota, pat ja tai ir kolekciju piekļuve, lai skatītu jautājumus vai informācijas paneļus, kas izmanto šos datus."

#: frontend/src/metabase/admin/permissions/components/DataPermissionsHelp/DataPermissionsHelp.tsx:95
msgid "Schema or table ‘View data’ levels"
msgstr "Shēmas vai tabulas ‘Skatīt datus’ līmeņi"

#: frontend/src/metabase/admin/permissions/components/DataPermissionsHelp/DataPermissionsHelp.tsx:102
msgid "The group can view all data for that schema or table."
msgstr "Grupa var skatīt visus datus šajā shēmā vai tabulā."

#: frontend/src/metabase/admin/permissions/components/DataPermissionsHelp/DataPermissionsHelp.tsx:109
msgid "\"No self-service\" works like it does for databases, except here it is scoped to individual schemas or tables."
msgstr "\"Nav pašapkalpošanās\" darbojas tāpat kā datubāzēm, tikai šeit tas attiecas uz atsevišķām shēmām vai tabulām."

#: frontend/src/metabase/admin/permissions/components/DataPermissionsHelp/DataPermissionsHelp.tsx:115
msgid "Row and column security (Pro)"
msgstr "Rindu un kolonnu drošība (Pro)"

#: frontend/src/metabase/admin/permissions/components/DataPermissionsHelp/DataPermissionsHelp.tsx:116
msgid "Lets you specify row and column-level permissions. Can be set up via user attributes and SSO."
msgstr "Ļauj norādīt rindu un kolonnu līmeņa atļaujas. Var iestatīt, izmantojot lietotāju atribūtus un SSO."

